# Product Modularization

**Config** (`deploy/config.yaml`): `edition`, `modules`, `roles_enabled`, `dashboard_layout`, **`locale`** (`zh-TW` \| `en`).

Presets: `deploy/presets/personal.yaml`, `professional.yaml`. Locale set at buyer onboarding; immutable in app UI.

**Backend:**

```text
core/deployment.py, capabilities.py, db.py (SQLAlchemy)
alembic/
modules/{inventory,orders,analytics}/
repositories/postgres/   # PG only — no mongo/
schemas/product/, models/product/
```

`main.py`: conditional routers by module. `GET /api/deployment` → modules, capabilities, **locale**.

**Frontend:** i18n (`react-i18next` or similar); load **one** locale from deployment config at startup — no language picker for merchants.

**Repositories:** `StockRepository`, `OrderRepository`; services never use raw SQL in routes.

**Avoid:** `MONGO_URI`; `staff`/`guest` roles; UI-only module hides; v1 `tea` schemas on product branch.
